<h1>Hi there! ッ</h1>
<div   class="twocolumn">
<p> Welcome to my little corner of the internet. I work at <a href="http://www.geodan.nl/research">Geodan Research</a> as a UxDesigner/tinkerer. During the years I've done all kinds of fun stuff and this site is an attempt to collect the most interesting ones. All the projects listed here are either built or designed by me. You are free to use and extend them, though it would be nice if you let <a href="twitter.com/stvno">me</a> know if you do something nice with it. I tend to work on the edge of (browser-) technology, as such it is recommended to use Chrome or Firefox, though the videos should be fine for everyone. Click on the brightly coloured bars for the goodies.</p>
<p>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://github.com/stvno/">GitHub</a></li>
<li><a href="https://twitter.com/stvno/">Twitter</a></li>
<li><a href="http://wiki.osgeo.org/wiki/User:Stvn">OSGeo</a></li>
</ul>
<span style=" display:inline-block; 
